{"tid":1887965,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情重創中國零售需求 Adidas銷售額跌85%","createTime":"2020-02-20T02:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T02:27:12.000Z","uid":271829,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee87336a8e8fd0ee5a1b4278b8baa63a932bdc47","tid":1887965,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:12:22.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續，影響中國本土消費。德國運動品牌Adidas及Puma指，疫情對生意造成衝擊，兩間公司被逼關閉門市以避免疫情蔓延。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》引述Adidas內部電郵指，自1月25日（年初一）以來，公司在中國的銷售額下跌85%，事實上，Adidas月初已表示武漢肺炎對業務產生負面衝擊，已關閉位於中國的大部份分店。Adidas中國官網上出現減價優惠，2月17日至23日期間會員訂購貨品以半價發售。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述Puma則指今年首季銷售及利潤均會下跌，估計今年實際盈利將較原先預期差。報道指，有關當局採取嚴厲措施應對疫情，不少企業均鼓勵員工留家，令現時很多商場及餐廳只有很少人流，現時Puma過半中國outlet亦已暫停營業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200219/large/1582105911_c322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200219%2Flarge%2F1582105911_c322.jpg&h=0e81d775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩間公司均指，疫情下減少亞太區內旅遊，影響公司在區內的業務表現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200219/UDK3JY475556MIZB3MBRLDCYK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200219%2FUDK3JY475556MIZB3MBRLDCYK4%2F&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5BA11HdiY488GD%2FHa51CVEA%3D&h=11227256\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200219%2FUDK3JY475556MIZB3MBRLDCYK4%2F&h=3701815a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200219/UDK3JY475556MIZB3MBRLDCYK4/</a>"},{"pid":"02d39726884801c0442a5ad56c2df869bf5e614e","tid":1887965,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奶呀奶"},{"pid":"89aad0a08c2b97e884ba4c3962147b30dc8ea04d","tid":1887965,"uid":20414,"like":1